  </p>
  <section class="card content-block">
    <h2>Outcome</h2>
    <p>Through structured critique and repeated refinement, I defined:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>A clear on-screen information hierarchy</li>

      <li>Simplified visibility rules</li>
      <li>
        Agreed principles for how data should surface during the live session
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      The result was a coherent, board-aligned design direction supported by
      sophisticated Figma prototypes, ready to be tested in a simulated group
      environment. <span style="font-size:24px;">üéâ</span>
    </p>
  </section>
